_:Nfd97eb595e814b80b4a2b32e63864c11 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Selvarani Elahi has worked for <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.lgcgroup.com/\"><abbr title=\"LGC is an international life sciences measurement and testing company and has been home to the UK Government Chemist for more than 100 years.\">LGC</abbr>,</a> a life sciences research and testing company, since 1991. Her first role was as a scientific officer in the Food and Nutrition Group. Since then Selvarani has worked in a number of different roles in food and agricultural analysis. She joined the Government Chemist programme in 2011 as Deputy Government Chemist.</p>\n\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
